ISLAMABAD, Jul 09 (APP):Prime Minister’s Coordinator on Information, Broadcasting and Khyber Pakhtunkhwa Affairs, Ikhtiar Wali Khan, has said that movements are not driven by emotions alone—they rise on the foundation of trust, unity, and principled leadership.
In a post on X  on Wednesday, Ikhtiar Wali Khan remarked that “How can those who are unsure of their own standing bear the weight of a movement that still lives in dreams?”
